translation[11]{c,v,t}:
  2,6,Chisimu aŵala ŵakanile; yalumope kwa jamanjao mwatetele kapena nkatetela ngakulupililape
  2,7,"Allah ŵadindile chidindo m’mitima mwao ni m’mawiwi mwao, soni m’meso mwao mwana chisiŵilo, basi tachipata jamanjao ilagasyo yekulungwa nnope"
  2,8,"Soni chilikati cha ŵandu pana (achinakunaku) ŵakutiji: “Tukulupilile mwa Allah ni Lisiku Lyambesi.” Kutendaga nganaŵa ŵakulupilila"
  2,9,"Akuntenda chinyengo Allah ni aŵala ŵakulupilile, ni pangali ŵaakwanyenga ikaŵeje achimisyene, ni ngakulimanyilila"
  2,10,"M’mitima mwao mwana ulwele; sano Allah niŵajonjechesye ulweleo, basi tachipata jamanjao ilagasyo yakupoteka nnope ligongo lyakuŵechetaŵecheta kwao yaunami"
  2,11,"Soni naga asalilidwemo kuti: “Nkawatanganyaga pachilambo.” Akasatiji: “Chisimutu uwwe niŵakwilanya.”"
  2,12,"Manyililani yanti ŵanganyao chisimu chene niŵali ŵakuwatanganya, nambo ngakulimanyilila"
  2,13,"Soni naga asalilidwemo kuti: “Kulupililani yatite pakulupilila ŵandu ŵane.” Akasatiji: “Ana tukulupilile yatite pakulupilila ŵawawate?” Manyililani yanti ŵanganyao chisimu chene niŵali ŵakuwawata, nambo ngakupata kumanyilila"
  2,14,"Soni naga asimene ni aŵala ŵakulupilile, akasatiji: “Tukulupilile,” nambo pati apite pa kasyepela ku mashetani gajao, akasatiji: “Chisimu uwwe tulinamwe, uwwetu tukuŵa tuli nkwatenda chipongwe.”"
  2,15,"Allah chachalipila pa chipongwe chaocho, ni chiŵalechelele nkusokonechela mwaomo achiyumbagayumbaga"
  2,16,"Jamanjao ni aŵalaŵala ŵasagwile kusokonechela pakusumanya ni chongoko, nambo kusumanya kwaoko nganikwajonjechesya (chilichose), soni nganaŵa ŵakongoka"